dc_description_s:
This polygon shapefile represents the political boundaries for the 113th United States congressional districts. The official membership is current as of August 18, 2014. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. U.S. 113th Congressional Districts provides the locations of congressional districts, primarily for national planning applications.

 ESRI and U.S. Census Bureau Geography Division. (2014). United States 113th Congressional Districts, 2014. ESRI.
